# Practicum AI-Craft вЂ” Cursor Project Rules

## Project Overview
Banner/layout generator for Yandex Practicum marketing team. Creates multi-format banner exports (PNG/JPG ZIP) from a visual editor with live Canvas preview.

**Stack:** Vanilla JS (ES Modules, no bundler), HTML5 Canvas 2D API, CSS Custom Properties, deployed as static site on Yandex Cloud Object Storage.

**No frameworks. No React. No TypeScript. No npm. No build step.**
All JS files are native ES modules loaded directly by the browser via `<script type="module">`.

