## Fonts
Yandex Sans family: YS Text, YS Display, YS Text Cond, YS Text Wide, YS Display Cond, YS Display Wide, YS Logotype, Yandex Serif Display.
Weights: Thin(100)вЂ“Black(900). Mappings in constants.js: FONT_NAME_TO_WEIGHT / FONT_WEIGHT_TO_NAME.
Font files: /font/{family}/{family}-{weight}.woff2 (and .ttf).

## Assets
- Logos: /logo/{black|white}/{ru|kz|en}/{main|long|mono}.svg
- 3D assets: /assets/3d/{icons|logos|numbers|other|shapes|sign|tech|yandex}/NN.webp
- Photos: /assets/photo/pro/NN.webp
- Assets are scanned dynamically by assetScanner.js вЂ” just add files to folders.

## Themes
Dark theme (default): CSS variables in `:root`
Light theme: overrides in `[data-theme="light"]`
Toggle stored in localStorage('theme'), applied via `data-theme` attr on `<html>`.

## i18n
Two languages: RU (default), EN. Keys in src/utils/i18n.js.
HTML elements with `data-i18n="key"` are auto-translated.
Use `t('key')` function in JS code.

## Persistence
All user data in localStorage:
- `default-values` вЂ” user's default settings
- `sizes-config` вЂ” custom size presets
- `format-multipliers` вЂ” per-format size adjustments
- `adminBackgrounds` вЂ” admin background library
- `theme` вЂ” dark/light
- `brandName` вЂ” brand name displayed in header
- `figma_token` вЂ” Figma Personal Access Token
- `admin_password` вЂ” admin panel password (plaintext)

## Testing
No test framework. Manual testing only. After any change:
1. Check all 3 preview canvases render correctly
2. Test narrow (1080Г—1920), square (1080Г—1080), wide (1920Г—720) formats
3. Test export PNG/JPG
4. Test light/dark theme
5. Test RU/EN language switch
